Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.87,0:22:48.88,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(120,0)\blur3.5\fax-0.2}舞动于夜空的苍月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:53.13,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}耀眼的世界穿过云霄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:22:57.34,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}如今奏响旅程的号角
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.34,0:23:01.55,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,800)}{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}将愿望传播至彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:13.65,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}无形的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:17.95,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}若能渗透于月光之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:22.53,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.15}是你心中的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:26.45,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}如今 随风飘逝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.37,0:23:31.13,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}明天就试着展翅高飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:35.96,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}就如曾经你所期望的那般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.96,0:23:42.35,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}你能听到吗 那光辉的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.72,0:23:48.31,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}舞动于夜空的苍月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.31,0:23:53.02,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a90}耀眼的世界穿过云霄
